project_descr: Initiation Plan: Market Transformation for Sustainable Rural Housing Project

outputs.output_descr: The objective of this initiation plan (IP) is to develop a full project document for a UNDP/GEF project aiming at transforming the rapidly growing rural housing sector in Uzbekistan towards a more sustainable and low-carbon development pathway by designing, piloting and scaling-up a green mortgage market mechanism, which will boost the demand for low-carbon housing among the Uzbek rural population.
